{"tid":109474,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完條片先知原來湯洛雯咁正","createTime":"2017-02-06T03:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T18:25:16.000Z","uid":49648,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f266cc9009f70bce71d8da9e02e827847fda25c7","tid":109474,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170205/bkn-20170205180133147-0205_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170205%2Fbkn-20170205180133147-0205_00862_001.html&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=be5c4f9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170205/bkn-20170205180133147-0205_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n無綫藝人湯洛雯（靚湯）形象斯文，主持資訊節目《學是學非》則展現搞笑活潑一面，成為大批宅男的模範女友。下星期就是情人節，Sweet爆的靚湯在今集東網巨星節目《區區有女神》特別版中充當粉絲的一日情人，大玩「女友主觀鏡頭」慰藉單身男，令觀眾猶如跟靚湯拍拖一樣！靚湯拖實「你」手重遊她兒時長大的大埔區，餵「你」食豆腐花、豬扒麵，又送上愛心頸巾，收到「你」送的玫瑰花後更閉眼索吻，嘩嘩嘩！ Sweet到爆呀！ <br />\n<br />\n湯洛雯更在大埔區「生擒」幾位年輕男士，拎起幾位「是非精」的相片，包括黃心穎、張秀文、李佳芯、梁嘉琪、麥美恩及自己，叫男士選出最佳女朋友。究竟靚湯魅力能否迷倒幾位男士？今集節目咁精彩，靚湯趁情人節前大派福利，無論你係咪單身，都要記得星期三晚黐實東網巨星喇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d0b44b6328a568558e84b28f4192ba3604e629","tid":109474,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e916ea2a74d9e2f23f34101d9347a4f1b4506c","tid":109474,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fY5ok3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfY5ok3.gif&h=a108bcc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbf0af43dfc97987445bcdca2df55a75ca374667","tid":109474,"uid":33104,"like":0,"